data.title: ZIP Codes in Salt Lake County, Utah
data.meta_description: Access 59 comprehensive ZIP Code datasets for Salt Lake County, Utah, providing detailed geographic and demographic insights.
data.text:
Access a comprehensive dataset of ZIP Codes for Salt Lake County, Utah, specifically designed for GIS professionals. This dataset includes detailed information on 59 ZIP Code Tabulation Areas (ZCTAs), providing key data such as land area, water area, and precise latitude and longitude coordinates. Useful for a wide range of applications from urban planning to logistics, these datasets are structured to aid in accurate and efficient data analysis and mapping. Noteworthy ZIP Codes such as 84050, 84074, 84071, and 84604 illustrate the diversity in land and water area across the county, serving as a vital resource for geographic data assessment and project planning in Utah.
